# Four tall towers

24:41.880 --> 24:43.600
# That train by esteem

24:43.600 --> 24:46.800
# Of the cliff corner view
of the school of our dreams

24:46.800 --> 24:48.560
# We came here as girls

24:48.560 --> 24:50.400
# To be women of the world

24:50.400 --> 24:52.840
# And we'll do so with prosperity. #

24:52.840 --> 24:54.240
LAUGHTER
